// ============================================================================
// BALANCED CONFIG EXAMPLE
// ============================================================================
//
// A middle-ground between capital preservation and opportunity capture.
// All five strategies are enabled with moderate position sizes and filters.
// A good starting point for users with some Polymarket experience.
//
// Good for: wallets of $100–$300, stable market conditions.
//
// To use: copy this file to src/config.rs, then `cargo build --release`.
// ============================================================================

